OL,3,CRiver City actor Iain Robertson to be
OL,4,Csentenced after being convicted of rape
OL,6,FActor Iain Robertson is due to be
OL,7,Fsentenced on Thursday after being
OL,8,Ffound guilty of raping one woman and
OL,9,Fassaulting others.
OL,11,FThe former River City star was
OL,12,Fconvicted last month of a total of
OL,13,Ffive offences against a number of
OL,14,Fwomen between 2004 and 2019.
OL,16,FThe 45-year-old is due to be sentenced
OL,17,Fat the High Court in Edinburgh.
OL,19,FThe rape occurred some time between
OL,20,F2018 and 2019.
