OL,3,CRiver City actor Iain Robertson to be
OL,4,Csentenced after being convicted of rape
OL,6,FDuring the trial at the High Court in
OL,7,FGlasgow, the woman told the court
OL,8,FRobertson had sex with her despite her
OL,9,Fmaking clear she was not consenting,
OL,10,Fand described going "limp" when he was
OL,11,Fon top of her.
OL,13,FGiving evidence during the trial,
OL,14,FRobertson said he was "no angel" but
OL,15,Fdenied any wrongdoing.
OL,17,FHe said he is "aware" of when a woman
OL,18,Fis consenting to sex, and that he is
OL,19,F"sensitive" enough to know about non-
OL,20,Fverbal communication.
